# http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/QuantityValue
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/QuantityValue> <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#Class> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/QuantityValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Numeric value with explicit unit of measure (qudt:numericValue + qudt:hasUnit). Allows representing physical quantities such as energy (kWh/m²·year), emissions (kgCO2/m²·year), power (kW), area (m²), percentage, etc."@en .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/QuantityValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Valor numérico con unidad de medida explícita (qudt:numericValue + qudt:hasUnit). Permite representar magnitudes físicas como energía (kWh/m²·año), emisiones (kgCO2/m²·año), potencia (kW), superficie (m²), porcentaje, etc."@es .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/QuantityValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#isDefinedBy> <http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/> .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/QuantityValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Quantity value"@en .
<http://qudt.org/schema/qudt/QuantityValue> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label> "Valor de cantidad"@es .
